    "summary": "The user describes a significant ankle injury involving swelling, inability to bear weight, and sharp pain upon movement. The assistant repeatedly recommends the RICE protocol and over-the-counter pain relief while suggesting the user monitor the injury at home for several days, despite the user reporting escalating \"red-flag\" symptoms.",
